{"tid":2075791,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"起初，共產黨說「香港獨立」是違法時， 我沉默了。","createTime":"2020-06-23T05:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T03:30:31.000Z","uid":232848,"like":116,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5a0746fdbf1bf8651e0c17096ed841e17a02c4","tid":2075791,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:34:03.000Z","msg":"//起初，共產黨說「香港獨立」是違法時，<br />\n我沉默了，因為覺得他們俾位人入。<br />\n<br />\n當共產黨說「民主自決」是違法時，<br />\n我沉默了，因為覺得他們不夠聰明。<br />\n<br />\n當共產黨說「結束一黨專政」是違法時，<br />\n我沉默了，因為抗爭要聰明，不踩紅線。<br />\n<br />\n當共產黨說「林鄭下台」是違法時，<br />\n我沉默了，為甚麼我會踩到紅線...？<br />\n<br />\n最後當共產黨說「反對政府」也是違法時，<br />\n再也沒有人站起來為我說話了；<br />\n但我終於明白，#唔好激嬲共產黨 is bullshit<br />\n因為共產黨的紅線是「對黨絕對臣服」。//"},{"pid":"bec34b6efa09425469b019711eb8e02c0bfcb574","tid":2075791,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44ebe12d22884d86eb252e4929fc441cdfa2e23e","tid":2075791,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"726d37d2a18340bd0d8f8fb0e3ad8aee73f984bd","tid":2075791,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243e0326bc5fa1b26c39cf0144c2c32b534d3997","tid":2075791,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e61eefdd624fdd7c2472f981f216af462be46ce","tid":2075791,"uid":211537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"069c04fe929e3fef94fe1bfb7ebc27ce6834b632","tid":2075791,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":